longBusinessSummary: Inception Mining, Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, production, and development of mineral properties in the United States. It primarily explores for gold deposits. The company holds interest in the Clavo Rico mine located on the 200-hectare Clavo Rico Concession, is which located in southern Honduras. Inception Mining, Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Murray, Utah.
